Class TitanBlueprintsTransaction

  • java.lang.Object

    public abstract class TitanBlueprintsTransaction
extends Object
implements TitanTransaction
    Blueprints specific implementation of TitanTransaction. Provides utility methods that wrap Titan calls with Blueprints terminology.

    Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)

      • addVertex

        public TitanVertex addVertex(Object id)
        Creates a new vertex in the graph with the given vertex id. Note, that an exception is thrown if the vertex id is not a valid Titan vertex id or if a vertex with the given id already exists. Only accepts long ids - all others are ignored.

        Custom id setting must be enabled via the configuration option GraphDatabaseConfiguration.ALLOW_SETTING_VERTEX_ID.

        Use TitanId.toVertexId(long) to construct a valid Titan vertex id from a user id.

        Specified by:
        addVertex in interface com.tinkerpop.blueprints.Graph
        Parameters:
        id - vertex id of the vertex to be created
        Returns:
        New vertex
